      "content": "8-12 Hz? that's super low. i definitely felt something in that range earlier. \n\nif i wanted to actually target a specific cell, how would i calculate the exact frequency for a storm of a certain size? like if the cell diameter is x, is there a formula to find the resonant frequency so i don't just make the wind pick up more instead of calming it down?",
